{"type":"compaction","id":"4dbd0327","parentId":"99243881","timestamp":"2026-05-10T12:53:01.773Z","summary":"## Goal\nConfigure the assistant/system so every reply and progress update follows the user’s required Thai format, enforced by real config/source changes rather than relying only on AI memory. Also make Hermes behave like this assistant “ทุกอย่าง” including form, mode analysis, tool/MCP gate, footer/session display, token-saving/session behavior, and now automatic temporary monitoring jobs for long-running/waiting SocratiCode tasks that notify completion and delete themselves/no junk files.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- User wants replies in exact header format: `🧑🏼‍💻[GPT 5.5] [คำถามทั่วไป] 🧑🏼‍💻`\n- Footer now includes short session form: `Session: (8%)` after RTK.\n- `Tokens:` must reflect real overall API/model context usage including hidden/system/tool/history context, not only user-typed text.\n- `Cache:` means cache hit percentage for reused context; not the same as Session.\n- `Session:` means current context/session usage percentage.\n- Do not change the user’s form.\n- Every progress/status message must also follow the required form.\n- Before any tool / MCP / command in every message: must first analyze mode and list tools/MCP/commands to be used.\n- For “หมวดทำงาน”, assistant must first state category, tools/NCT/MCP to use, and what will be changed before executing.\n- Hermes-related work requires explicit permission first; user previously granted “อนุญาต”.\n- Must use SocratiCode before code/config work when applicable.\n- Prefer low-token workflow: search/excerpt/truncate over full logs/files.\n- User wants rolling 2-session retention: keep latest session + previous session as backup; when a new session is created, delete only the oldest so 2 remain.\n- For Hermes work, user explicitly requires writing/implementing inside Hermes, not referencing/depending on files in the assistant/OpenClaw workspace.\n- New preference: when SocratiCode or similar background work is waiting/running, create an automatic temporary cron/job/monitor so user knows when it will finish or that it finished, then auto-delete the job/files after completion.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Added persistent progress-notification rule to `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/AGENTS.md`\n- [x] Added same rule to `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- [x] Confirmed inserted rules with `grep`\n- [x] Inspected Hermes/OpenClaw config and gateway code via SocratiCode/search\n- [x] Found `display.runtime_footer.enabled: false` in `/home/apinan/.hermes/config.yaml`\n- [x] Found `gateway/runtime_footer.py` only supports footer, not full required envelope\n- [x] Added backup files with suffix `.bak-response-envelope-20260510-191127`\n- [x] Added `enforce_response_envelope()` to `/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/runtime_footer.py`\n- [x] Patched `/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/run.py` to call `enforce_response_envelope()` before final send\n- [x] Enabled config block `display.response_envelope.enabled: true` in `/home/apinan/.hermes/config.yaml`\n- [x] Ran `py_compile` checks successfully\n- [x] Tested envelope wrapping and fixed emoji ZWJ issue from `🧑🏼💻` to `🧑🏼‍💻`\n- [x] Patched `runtime_footer.py` so valid headers must start like `🧑🏼‍💻[MODEL] [CATEGORY] 🧑🏼‍💻`\n- [x] Updated generated header format to `🧑🏼‍💻[GPT 5.5] [สรุป] 🧑🏼‍💻`\n- [x] Added footer/session preference in behavior: `Session: (8%)`\n- [x] Explained `Cache` vs `Session` to user.\n- [x] Saved rolling 2-session retention preference in `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- [x] User pointed out assistant used tools before analyzing command; assistant acknowledged error.\n- [x] Added strict Tool/MCP Gate to `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/AGENTS.md`\n- [x] Added strict Tool/MCP Gate to `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- [x] SocratiCode indexed `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace`\n- [x] SocratiCode impact check showed `AGENTS.md` and `MEMORY.md` blast radius 0.\n- [x] SocratiCode index updated after editing `AGENTS.md` and `MEMORY.md`\n- [x] Gateway appears recovered/running after earlier restart/draining; later `session_status` showed gateway uptime increasing.\n- [x] Added Hermes-native override rules to `/home/apinan/.hermes/SOUL.md`\n- [x] Created `/home/apinan/.hermes/AGENTS.md` as Hermes-native project context/backup rules\n- [x] Confirmed `/home/apinan/.hermes/SOUL.md` and `/home/apinan/.hermes/AGENTS.md` contain the override rules.\n- [x] Checked SocratiCode `/home/apinan/.hermes` status multiple times; index is green but another process is still indexing.\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Implement automatic temporary SocratiCode/background monitor job creation for waiting tasks, with completion notification and auto-cleanup/no junk files.\n- [ ] Apply that behavior to both assistant workflow and Hermes-native behavior as requested.\n- [ ] Wait for or manage SocratiCode indexing for `/home/apinan/.hermes`; latest status: `6851 of 7003 discovered`, `Chunks stored: 64575 (partial)`, `ANOTHER PROCESS (PID 460386) IS ACTIVELY INDEXING this project.`\n\n### Blocked\n- No hard blocker, but `/home/apinan/.hermes` SocratiCode indexing is still running in another process, so search confirmation is not 100% complete.\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Use system-side enforcement**: User explicitly rejected relying only on AI self-discipline; patch must be in source/config.\n- **Do not use `post_llm_call` for mutation**: Hermes docs say `post_llm_call` return values are ignored.\n- **Patch send path instead**: `gateway/run.py` is the final response path where footer/envelope can be enforced.\n- **Preserve reply tags**: `enforce_response_envelope()` preserves `[[reply_to...]]` tags before wrapping.\n- **Exact format correction required**: Header must be bracketed exactly like `🧑🏼‍💻[GPT 5.5] [คำถามทั่วไป] 🧑🏼‍💻`.\n- **Tool/MCP Gate required**: Every message must first classify mode and disclose intended tools/MCP/commands before using them.\n- **Hermes must be standalone**: User does not want Hermes to read/use assistant/OpenClaw workspace rule files because names like OpenClaw would confuse him.\n- **Session retention preference**: Keep rolling 2 sessions: latest + previous backup; delete oldest only when a new one exists.\n- **Temporary monitor jobs**: For long-running SocratiCode/background waits, create a temporary cron/job/monitor, notify when done, then delete the job/files automatically to avoid junk.\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Before any tool use, state mode and exact tool/MCP/command plan.\n2. For new implementation, ask/confirm permission if needed, then use `hermes-permission skill → SocratiCode → inspect Hermes-native locations → impact → edit → check`.\n3. Design minimal temporary monitor job mechanism for SocratiCode/background waits, preferably self-deleting after success/failure notification.\n4. Implement in Hermes-native files only under `/home/apinan/.hermes`, not `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace`.\n5. Add/update assistant-side rule/memory only if explicitly allowed/needed for “ทั้งมึง”, while avoiding conflict with Hermes-native requirement.\n6. Run syntax/compile checks and low-token verification.\n7. Continue checking `/home/apinan/.hermes` SocratiCode index until complete, then search-confirm the new Hermes rules.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Latest user request: “ให้ทำทั้ง ทั้งมึงแล้วก็คือเมตรสร้างต่ออัตโนมัติถ้ามีอะไรต้องรอแบบนี้แต่ว่าหลังจากที่เสร็จก็ต้องลบทิ้งไม่เก็บพวกไฟล์ขยะ”\n- User wants automatic job/cron-like monitoring for SocratiCode waits, with auto-deletion after completion.\n- Latest SocratiCode status for `/home/apinan/.hermes`: `Status: green`, `Indexed chunks: 64575`, `ANOTHER PROCESS (PID 460386) IS ACTIVELY INDEXING this project`, `Files indexed so far: 6851 of 7003 discovered`.\n- Previous Hermes-native modified files:\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/runtime_footer.py`\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/run.py`\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/config.yaml`\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/SOUL.md`\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/AGENTS.md`\n- Workspace files also modified earlier:\n  - `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/AGENTS.md`\n  - `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md`\n- `apply_patch` failed due sandbox: `Path escapes sandbox root (/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace): /home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/runtime_footer.py`\n- Used Python exact-replace fallback to edit Hermes files.\n- `find -printf` via RTK failed: `rtk find: unknown flag '-printf', ignored`; `/usr/bin/find` worked.\n- Earlier `openclaw gateway restart` exited with code 1 and no output; later `session_status` showed gateway running.\n- Must preserve the strict response form and tool gate in every progress message.\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\nให้เพิ่มกฎถาวรว่าเมื่อมีงานที่ต้องรอระบบ/ดัชนี/build/test/process นาน ให้สร้าง cron/job เฝ้าและแจ้งเมื่อเสร็จอัตโนมัติ พร้อมลบตัวเอง/ไม่ทิ้งไฟล์ขยะ ทั้งฝั่ง workspace และ Hermes\n\n## Early Progress\n- โหลดกฎ `hermes-permission` และ `socraticode-code`\n- ใช้ SocratiCode ตรวจสถานะ/impact ก่อนแก้:\n  - `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace` status green\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes` status green\n  - impact ของ `AGENTS.md`, `MEMORY.md`, `SOUL.md`, `AGENTS.md` เป็น 0\n- อ่านไฟล์กฎที่เกี่ยวข้อง แล้วแก้เพิ่มกฎ auto-wait-job ใน 4 ไฟล์:\n  - `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/AGENTS.md`\n  - `/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md`\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/SOUL.md`\n  - `/home/apinan/.hermes/AGENTS.md`\n- ยืนยันด้วย `grep` พบกฎใหม่ครบทั้ง 4 ไฟล์\n- อัปเดต SocratiCode index ของ workspace สำเร็จ; Hermes update ถูก skip เพราะมีอีก process indexing อยู่\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- เพราะ Hermes SocratiCode index/update ยังมี process ค้าง จึงสร้าง cron ชื่อ `watch-hermes-socraticode-index-self-cleanup`\n- cron job id: `8535c5ca-15ff-416e-9192-8410aa55699e`\n- schedule: ทุก 120 วินาที, `sessionTarget: isolated`, delivery announce ไป Telegram user เดิม\n- payload สั่งให้ตรวจ `socraticode__codebase_status` ของ `/home/apinan/.hermes`; ถ้ายัง indexing ให้ `NO_REPLY`; ถ้าเสร็จให้แจ้งเจ้านายและ `cron remove` job ตัวเอง\n- ล่าสุดเช็ก `cron list` พบ job อยู่จริง และ `socraticode__codebase_status /home/apinan/.hermes` เป็น green, indexed chunks 71023, file watcher active, graph built ล่าสุด 64s ago\n\n<read-files>\n/home/apinan/.hermes/MEMORY.md\n/home/apinan/.hermes/USER.md\n/home/apinan/.hermes/config.yaml\n/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/run.py\n/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/runtime_footer.py\n/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/skills/hermes-permission/SKILL.md\n/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/skills/socraticode-code/SKILL.md\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/apinan/.hermes/AGENTS.md\n/home/apinan/.hermes/SOUL.md\n/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/AGENTS.md\n/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"e1692e13","tokensBefore":40767,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/apinan/.hermes/MEMORY.md","/home/apinan/.hermes/USER.md","/home/apinan/.hermes/config.yaml","/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/run.py","/home/apinan/.hermes/hermes-agent/gateway/runtime_footer.py","/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/skills/hermes-permission/SKILL.md","/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/skills/socraticode-code/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":["/home/apinan/.hermes/AGENTS.md","/home/apinan/.hermes/SOUL.md","/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/AGENTS.md","/mnt/c/Users/Apinan/Dropbox/owen-workspace/MEMORY.md"]},"fromHook":false}
