{"type":"message","id":"cac90cc8","parentId":"3ff15432","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:03:37.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is upset because I didn't clearly say that the work is \"เสร็จแล้ว\" (completed). Looking back at my previous responses, I gave a progress summary but didn't explicitly state that the RTK integration work is complete. Let me address this clearly now.\n\nLet me also check the cron job situation - the monitor job might still be running since the graph was still building. Let me check if it has completed and cleaned up.\n\nThe user is right - I should have clearly stated \"เสร็จแล้วครับเจ้านาย\" at the beginning. My last response said the graph was still building and a cron was watching, but I didn't circle back to confirm everything is done.\n\nLet me check the current state:\n1. RTK rules added to AGENTS.md/SOUL.md ✅\n2. Config changed to rtk_label: enabled ✅\n3. Skill created ✅\n4. YAML valid ✅\n5. All checks passed ✅\n\nI should just apologize and clearly state everything is done. Let me also check if the cron has cleaned itself up.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_g427sw1w","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama-pay","model":"deepseek-v4-pro:cloud","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778418160486,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1778418197073"}}
